name: Dainty Sterling Skull Necklace
description:
A sweet shiny sterling silver over rhodium bead is thread through a 16 inch sterling silver chain.

name: Sterling Silver My Sister and Me Necklace
description:
The glass cabochon uses original artwork and features 2 sisters the eldest sister has her arm round the little sister-adorable.

The cabochon is set in a sterling silver setting and attached to a matching 16 inch sterling silver chain

18 inch chain also available for no additional cost.

The cabochon measures 18mm x 13mm


Comes with a lovely zebra print gift box too

name: Sterling Minimalist Cube Necklace- Dainty
description:

Note * Main Picture has  been taken close up to show detail

name: Sterling Surprise Inside Russian Doll Necklace
description:
When you open up this cute solid sterling silver Russian Doll pendant you will find another sweet russian doll nested within, just like how the Russian dolls are stacked. This sterling silver necklace is a great fun piece to own.

The Russian doll is made here in the Uk.
 It is 3D with great intricate details. 

Measurements:
Necklace - 18" sterling silver chain
Charm - 1" tall measuring from the hanging top loop

All components in this necklace are made with Sterling silver. 

Made to order- please allow up to 5 working days for desptach

name: Sterling Cheeky Squirrel In The Acorn Necklace
description:
A truly cute solid sterling silver acorn charm nested with a sweet brown squirrel. This sterling silver necklace is fun, sweet and will definitely bring a smile.

The acorn charm is made here in the Uk.
The squirrel is  sterling silver coated with brown enamel and is stored within the acorn and will surprise you when you open it up. 

Measurements:
Necklace - 16"  sterling silver chain
Charm - 0.75"

All components in this necklace are made with Sterling silver. 

Made to order please allow up to 5 working days for despatch
